  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个物流系统的核心流程图，从配送路线开始，经过追踪号处理，最后到仓库管理。我想用从左到右的布局。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，您说的追踪号处理是只出现一次，还是会有多个环节？比如扫描、更新状态这种。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有两个连续的追踪号节点——第一个是生成追踪号，第二个是实时更新位置信息，然后才进入车队管理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以流程是：配送路线 → 生成追踪号 → 更新位置信息 → 车队管理 → 仓库。我先把这几个节点按顺序连起来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了，五个节点从左到右依次连接：配送路线、追踪号生成、追踪号更新、车队管理、仓库。您看看结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，第二个和第三个节点的标签好像重复了，都是追踪号。第三个应该是更新后的追踪状态，但节点类型确实是追踪号没错。这样标注可以吗，还是我们需要区分一下？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我理解了，业务上是两个步骤但系统模块都是追踪号。如果保持技术架构视角，两个节点用相同标签是合理的；如果需要突出业务阶段，我可以加备注。您倾向哪种？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "保持技术架构视角吧，两个都是追踪号模块，只是调用时机不同。这样技术人员看流程图更清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下最终结构：起点是Logistics_DeliveryRoute，经过两次Logistics_TrackingNumber处理，再到Logistics_FleetManagement，终点是Logistics_Warehouse。共五个节点，四条连线，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这个流程。车队管理节点要放在仓库前面，因为货物先到车队调度，最后才入库。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
